|-------|---------------|
| Name | Founder first + last name |
| Company | Company name |
| Website | Company URL |
| Email | Verified email from Apollo |
| LinkedIn | Profile URL |
| Twitter | Handle (if active) |
| Video title | Loom video title |
| Loom URL | Raw loom.com/share/xxx link |
| Email sent | Date sent |
| LinkedIn sent | Date sent |
| Twitter sent | Date + type (reply / DM) |
| Reply received | Date + channel |
| Reply type | Positive / Question / Not now / No |
| GTM sent | Date GTM output sent |
| Call booked | Date |
| Outcome | Active / Closed / Dead |

### Key Metrics to Watch Weekly
- Videos recorded per day
- Emails sent per day
- Reply rate (target: 5–15%)
- Positive reply rate (target: 3–8%)
- Calls booked per week (target: 3–5)
- Loom open/view rate (track in Loom dashboard)

### What Good Looks Like
- 10 videos/day × 5 days = 50 touches/week
- 5% positive reply rate = 2–3 replies/day
- 30–40% of positive replies → calls = 1–2 calls/day
- 10 calls/week → 2–3 demos → 1 close

